{"履修期": "秋学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:;\">“The single greatest cause of difficulties in global business transactions is not a lack of technical expertise, hard work, or good intentions – it is a lack of ‘people skills’ for relating successfully with counterparts from other countries and cultures.” (<span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Working GlobeSmart</span>, Ernest Gundling)</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(38,38,38);\">As more and more our global markets expand and our workplaces become increasingly multi-ethnic, intercultural understanding and effective communication skills as well as interaction and integration among the people have become critical.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"margin:0in;font-size:12pt;font-family:;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(38,38,38);\">In this course, students will </span>develop intercultural competence – the ability to communicate and behave appropriate ways with those who are culturally different focusing on a multicultural business environment. <span style=\"background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">A</span><span style=\"background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">lso t</span><span style=\"background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">his course explores the challenges of working in a culturally diverse work force and the complexities of dealing with different traditions, l</span><span style=\"background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">anguages, </span><span style=\"background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">and value systems in order to collaborate across borders.</span></p>", "到達目標": "<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin:0in 0in 0in 14.2pt;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;text-indent:-14.2pt;\"><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">1.<span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-feature-settings:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">To develop skills, knowledge, and attitudes which are needed to function effectively personally and professionally</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin:0in 0in 0in 14.2pt;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;text-indent:-14.2pt;\"><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">2.<span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-feature-settings:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">To identify cultural gaps, analyze how they affect in business situations, and decide on strategies to bridge those gaps</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin:0in 0in 0in 14.2pt;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;text-indent:-14.2pt;\"><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">3.<span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-feature-settings:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">To recognize challenges of working virtually and identify the roots of miscommunication, and learn to minimize the barriers to effective communication</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin:0in 0in 0in 14.2pt;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;text-indent:-14.2pt;\"><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">4.<span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\";\"=\"roman';'\" style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;font-variant-alternates:normal;font-kerning:auto;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-feature-settings:normal;font-variation-settings:normal;font-variant-position:normal;font-stretch:normal;font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">To gain insights into why Japanese business people behave the way they do</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagr